name: Crystal Skull
description:
follow me on Instagram, Youtube and my website.

Crystal Skull

Suggested Weight: 1.0 - although aside from simply generating crystal skulls you can combine this with a number of unexpected things like people, fruit, abstract concepts, etc.

Suggested prompts

  • professional photo of cry5t415ku11 (druzy quartz), light bokeh, sharp focus, intricate detail

  • try adding terms like druzy, garnet, azurite, amethyst, calcite, quartz, opal, malachite, etc

  • cry5t415ku11 (druzy quartz) AND apple, light bokeh, sharp focus, intricate detail

Training

  • trained on ~30 images

  • Learning Rate: 0.005:1000, 0.001:2000, 0.0001:5000, 0.00005

  • Batch Size: 1

  • Gradient Steps: 1
